oyev]] (22 / 2), [[Oleg Kornienko]] {{flagicon|KAZ}} (19), [[Aslan Datdeyev]] (18 / 1), [[Igor Gorelov]] (9), [[Alan Agayev]] (7 / 1), [[Ali Alchagirov]] (7), [[Sergei Gorlukovich]] (5).<br />\n'''Midfielders:''' [[Igor Yanovskiy]] (29 / 2), [[Bakhva Tedeyev]] (28 / 10), [[Sergei Derkach]] (26 / 5), [[Mirjalol Qosimov]] {{flagicon|UZB}} (22 / 10), [[Georgi Botsiyev]] (9), [[Shamil Isayev]] (1), [[Zaza Revishvili]] {{flagicon|GEO}} (1).<br />\n'''Forwards:''' [[Anatoli Kanishchev]] (26 / 7), [[Mikhail Kavelashvili]] {{flagicon|GEO}} (24 / 12), [[Nazim Suleymanov]] {{flagicon|AZE}} (13 / 4), [[Tamerlan Sikoyev]] (3), [[Aslan Goplachev]] (2).<br />''(league appearances and goals listed in brackets)''\n\nOne own goal scored by [[Stanislav Bondarev]] ([[FC Zhemchuzhina Sochi]]).\n\n'''Manager:''' [[Valery Gazzaev]].\n\n'''Transferred out during the season:''' [[Igor Gorelov]] (to [[FC Dynamo-Gazovik Tyumen]]), [[Aslan Goplachev]], [[Shamil Isayev]] (both to [[PFC Spartak Nalchik]]).\n|- bgcolor=\"#DB0500\"\n| align=\"center\" width=\"700\" |<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"> '''2. FC Lokomotiv Moscow''' </span>\n|- bgcolor=\"#E8E8E8\"  \n| align=\"left\" width=\"700\" |\n'''Goalkeepers:''' [[Sergei Ovchinnikov (footballer born 1970)|Sergei Ovchinnikov]] (27), [[Khasanbi Bidzhiyev]] (3).<br />\n'''Defenders:''' [[Igor Chugainov]] (30 / 1), [[Andrei Solomatin]] (27 / 4), [[Sargis Hovhannisyan]] {{flagicon|ARM}} (23 / 2), [[Aleksei Arifullin]] (21), [[Oleg Pashinin]] {{flagicon|UZB}} (14), [[Sergei Gurenko]] {{flagicon|BLR}} (13), [[Vyacheslav Tsaryov]] (4).<br />\n'''Midfielders:''' [[Yuri Alekseevich Drozdov]] (30), [[Alexei Kosolapov]] (29 / 9), [[Yevgeni Kharlachyov]] (26 / 11), [[Oleg Elyshev]] (26 / 2), [[Aleksandr Smirnov (footballer, born 1968)|Aleksandr Smirnov]] (16 / 2), [[Ansar Ayupov]] (14 / 1), [[Vladimir Maminov]] {{flagicon|UZB}} (11 / 1), [[Yevgeni Kuznetsov (footballer born 1961)|Yevgeni Kuznetsov]] (10 / 1), [[Yuri Baturenko]] {{flagicon|TJK}} (3), [[Sergei 