yanov (footballer, born 1948)|Aleksandr Averyanov]]\n|-\n| [[FC Dynamo-Gazovik Tyumen]]\n| [[Aleksandr Bubnov]] (until March)<br />[[Sergei Rozhkov (footballer)|Sergei Rozhkov]] (March to April)<br />[[Aleksandr Irkhin]] (April to July)<br />[[Eduard Malofeyev]] (from August)\n|-\n|}\n\n==League standings==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|show_limit=5\n\n|team1=ALA|name_ALA=[[FC Alania Vladikavkaz|Spartak-Alania Vladikavkaz]]\n|team2=LOK|name_LOK=[[FC Lokomotiv Moscow|Lokomotiv Moscow]]\n|team3=SPA|name_SPA=[[FC Spartak Moscow|Spartak Moscow]]\n|team4=DYN|name_DYN=[[FC Dynamo Moscow|Dynamo Moscow]]\n|team5=TOR|name_TOR=[[FC Torpedo Moscow|Torpedo Moscow]]\n|team6=CSK|name_CSK=[[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]]\n|team7=ROT|name_ROT=[[FC Rotor Volgograd|Rotor Volgograd]]\n|team8=URA|name_URA=[[FC Uralmash Yekaterinburg|Uralmash Yekaterinburg]]\n|team9=KNC|name_KNC=[[FC KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny|KAMAZ Naberezhnye Chelny]]\n|team10=TKK|name_TKK=[[FC Tekstilshchik Kamyshin|Tekstilshchik Kamyshin]]\n|team11=CHE|name_CHE=[[FC Chernomorets Novorossiysk|Chernomorets Novorossiysk]]\n|team12=LNN|name_LNN=[[FC Lokomotiv Nizhny Novgorod|Lokomotiv N.N.]]\n|team13=ROS|name_ROS=[[FC Rostov|Rostselmash]]\n|team14=ZHE|name_ZHE=[[FC Zhemchuzhina Sochi|Zhemchuzhina Sochi]]\n|team15=KRY|name_KRY=[[FC Krylia Sovetov Samara|Krylia Sovetov Samara]]\n|team16=TYU|name_TYU=[[FC Tyumen|Dynamo-Gazovik Tyumen]]\n|win_ALA=22|draw_ALA=5|loss_ALA=3|gf_ALA=63|ga_ALA=21|status_ALA=C\n|win_LOK=20|draw_LOK=5|loss_LOK=5|gf_LOK=52|ga_LOK=23\n|win_SPA=19|draw_SPA=6|loss_SPA=5|gf_SPA=76|ga_SPA=26\n|win_DYN=16|draw_DYN=8|loss_DYN=6|gf_DYN=45|ga_DYN=29\n|win_TOR=16|draw_TOR=7|loss_TOR=7|gf_TOR=40|ga_TOR=30\n|win_CSK=16|draw_CSK=5|loss_CSK=9|gf_CSK=56|ga_CSK=34\n|win_ROT=11|draw_ROT=7|loss_ROT=12|gf_ROT=62|ga_ROT=49\n|win_URA=12|draw_URA=3|loss_URA=15|gf_URA=43|ga_URA=47\n|win_KNC=10|draw_KNC=8|loss_KNC=12|gf_KNC=34|ga_KNC=30\n|win_TKK=9|draw_TKK=7|loss_TKK=14|gf_TKK=37|g